@NODE INTRO "Introduction to Phone Pro Usa 2 "

Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~

PhoneProUSA is as easy as Jam/CD going `Baaaaaa.' - The actual usage of
this BaaaaaaaD utility is that of a simple nature; A utility to reflect
ones self. A utility to stabalise ones life into a peaceful and gifted
existence. Hmmmnn. Okay. If you make long distance calls over to America
(Phreakers!!) then this is the utility for you. It prompts you for a
three digit american dialling code like 907 which is alaska. So any american
dialling code you have and you want to know where it is you are (Phreaking?)
from then this utility will tell you. There is no need to dial the +01
code it automatically skips the 01 bit as it doesn't really need it.
 Okay. My address is down at the bottom for bug reports etc, also for
joining run the executable and look at the requester for Kei/Cyberdreams.

Although the above text may confuse you somewhat, even maffia/cd
can use it - so it can't be that hard!

